<view class="container">
<form bindsubmit="formBindsubmit">
  <view class="page-section">
    <view class="weui-cells__title">主密码</view>
    <view class="weui-cells weui-cells_after-title">
      <view class="weui-cell weui-cell_input">
        <input class="weui-input" name="title" auto-focus placeholder="输入主密码" name="password" />
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-box">你还未设置主密码,请设置主密码!</view>
    <view class="text-box">主密码是用来加密和解密的唯一依据,请牢记！主密码一旦设置以成功以后不可修改，也不提供找回功能！
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="btn-box" id="buttonContainer">
    <button type="primary" formType="submit" >确定</button>
  </view>
  </form>
</view>
<modal title="提示" hidden="{{modalHidden}}" confirm-text="确定"  cancel-text="取消" bindconfirm="modalBindaconfirm" bindcancel="modalBindaconfirm" >密码不能为空</modal>

